<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
    <head>
        <title>Sci-Hub | The Sequence of the Human Genome | 10.1126/science.1058040</title>
        <meta charset="UTF-8">
        <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width">
        <script src="//img.sci-hub.shop/scripts/jquery-3.6.0.min.js"></script>
    </head>
    <body>
    <script type = "text/javascript">
        
        var menu;
        var article;
        var position;
        function rollupi()
        {
            position = position - 2;
            menu.style.left = position.toString() + 'vw';
            article.style.left = (position + 20).toString() + 'vw';
            article.style.width = (80 - position).toString() + 'vw';
            if (position > -20)
                setTimeout(rollupi, 33);
            else
                document.getElementById('rollback').style.display = 'block';
        }
        function rollup()
        {
            $.get("//sci-hub.ren/rollup/on?rand=" + (Math.random() + 1).toString(36).substring(7));
            menu = document.getElementById('minu');
            article = document.getElementById('article');
            position = 0;
            rollupi();
        }
        function rollbacki()
        {
            position = position + 2;
            menu.style.left = position.toString() + 'vw';
            article.style.left = (position + 20).toString() + 'vw';
            article.style.width = (80 - position).toString() + 'vw';
            if (position < 0)
                setTimeout(rollbacki, 33);
        }
        function rollback()
        {
            $.get("//sci-hub.ren/rollup/off?rand=" + (Math.random() + 1).toString(36).substring(7));
            menu = document.getElementById('minu');
            article = document.getElementById('article');
            document.getElementById('rollback').style.display = 'none';
            document.getElementById('roll').style.display = 'block';
            position = -20;
            rollbacki();
        }

<head>
    <title>Sci-Hub | The Sequence of the Human Genome | 10.1126/science.1058040</title>
    <meta charset="UTF-8"/>
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width"/>
<script src="//img.sci-hub.shop/scihub/jquery-3.3.1.min.js"></script>
</head>
<body>
<script type = "text/javascript">
        function clip(element)
        {
          var $temp = $("<input>");
          $("body").append($temp);
          $temp.val($(element).text()).select();
          document.execCommand("copy");
          $temp.remove();
        }
</script>

            body {
                height: 100%;
                width: 100%;
                margin: 0;
                overflow: hidden;
            }
            div {
                font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, Roboto, Helvetica Neue, sans-serif;
            }

            #menu {
                width: 370px;
                height: 100%;
                position: fixed;
                z-index: 1;
                top: 0;
                left: 0;
                background-color: white;
                overflow-x: hidden;
            }

            #header {
                cursor: pointer;
            }
            #logo {
                background: url("//img.sci-hub.shop/scihub/ravenround.gif") no-repeat;
                width: 165px;
                height: 157px;
                margin-left: 18px;
            }
            #sci {
                background: #bbb;
                color: white;
                margin: 50px 0 0 10px;
                padding: 5px 20px 5px 25px;
                font-size: 38px;
            }
            #sci:hover {
                background: #b22222;
            }
            #motto {
                color: #999;
                margin: 18px 0 0 24px;
                font-size: 18px;
            }

            #buttons {
                margin-top: 30px;
